data.description: Come see this beautiful two story home with a stone front, landscaping and a swing two car garage located in the highly rated Mansfield ISD school district. The home features 4 bedrooms, 3 full and 1 half baths, 2 dining areas, an office or flex room on the first floor. The kitchen has a large island with bar top seating, a built in microwave, double ovens, a five burner gas cooktop, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and an eat in breakfast nook. The backyard features a private deck where you can enjoy the evenings outside and plenty of yard to enjoy. This home is close to shopping, dining and Walnut Creek Golf course.
